o work today,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even the GPS\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While authorities announced the code system last year and have beenmeeting with local residentsfor months to explain the restrictions, not everyone was aware.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"authorities\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"the code system\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"local residentsfor months\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"the restrictions\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"not everyone\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Officers patiently explained to visitors without the pass how to reach iconic Paris monuments without going through the restricted zone.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2151, \"end\": 2156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3374946710355986e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Officers\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2113}, {\"ngram\": \"the pass\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"the restricted zone\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had no idea we needed a QR code,\\\" said Takao Sakamoto, 55, who was denied access to the Eiffel Tower near the Bir Hakeim Metro station.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2254, \"end\": 2268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takao_Sakamoto\", \"score\": 0.9999998026915103, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Takao Sakamoto\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takao_Sakamoto\", \"dbpedia\":