icers\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"QR codes\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2630}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"the sight\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2703}, {\"ngram\": \"near-empty riverside boulevards\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2738}, {\"ngram\": \"normal times\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no one around!\\\"\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"sang a happy cyclist on a street he had largely to himself.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a happy cyclist\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"a street\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With police seemingly everywhere, another man walking past a riverside caf\\u00e9 with fewer than usual customers loudly quipped: \\\"You can leave your money and cell phones on the tables, there is definitely no thieves!\\\"\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 3082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2880}, {\"ngram\": \"another man\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"a riverside caf\\u00e9\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2944}, {\"ngram\": \"fewer than usual customers\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"your money and cell phones\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3034}, {\"ngram\": \"the tables\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"no thieves\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's surreal, it really feels like we are the only ones here,\\\" said Sarah Bartnicka from Canada.\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3153, \"end\": 3158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"score\": 0.8533135937481489, \"rank\": 0.17190188609142495, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q242